trans-unit.source: Contains methods and properties that are used to manage queries to the tracking data that is contained in the SQL database used by a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder og egenskaper som brukes til å behandle spørringer til sporing data som finnes i SQL-databasen som brukes av en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] SqlTrackingQuery provides methods and properties that you can use in order to access certain kinds of tracking data stored in a SQL database by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]SqlTrackingQuery gir metoder og egenskaper som kan brukes for å få tilgang til bestemte typer sporing av data som er lagret i SQL database <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: Access to this data is provided through <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects.
trans-unit.target: Har fått tilgang til disse dataene gjennom <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekter.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> to try to get a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ringe <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A>du kan prøve å hente en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>for en bestemt arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects that correspond workflow instances that have tracking data that matches a set of query parameters contained in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> that is passed as a parameter to the method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ringe <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A>å hente en samling av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekter som samsvarer med arbeidsflytforekomster som har sporing av data som samsvarer med et sett med spørring parametere i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions>som blir sendt som en parameter til metoden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A>

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> class for more information about the kind of tracking data available and see the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> class for more information about the kind of queries that can be performed.
trans-unit.target: Se den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>klasse for mer informasjon om hvilke sporing tilgjengelige data og se den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions>klasse for mer informasjon om hvilke spørringer som kan utføres.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery"> </xref> klasse.
